327    public static void writes_sample_jmhStub(InfraControl control, RawResults result, BenchmarkParams benchmarkParams, IterationParams iterationParams, ThreadParams threadParams, Blackhole blackhole, Control notifyControl, int startRndMask, SampleBuffer buffer, int targetSamples, long opsPerInv, int batchSize, PublishSubscriberWithResultBenchmarks_jmhType l_publishsubscriberwithresultbenchmarks0_G) throws Throwable {
328        long realTime = 0;
329        long operations = 0;
330        int rnd = (int)System.nanoTime();
331        int rndMask = startRndMask;
332        long time = 0;
333        int currentStride = 0;
334        do {
335            rnd = (rnd * 1664525 + 1013904223);
336            boolean sample = (rnd & rndMask) == 0;
337            if (sample) {
338                time = System.nanoTime();
339            }
340            for (int b = 0; b < batchSize; b++) {
341                if (control.volatileSpoiler) return;
342                l_publishsubscriberwithresultbenchmarks0_G.writes();
343            }
344            if (sample) {
345                buffer.add((System.nanoTime() - time) / opsPerInv);
346                if (currentStride++ > targetSamples) {
347                    buffer.half();
348                    currentStride = 0;
349                    rndMask = (rndMask << 1) + 1;
350                }
351            }
352            operations++;
353        } while(!control.isDone);
354        startRndMask = Math.max(startRndMask, rndMask);
355        result.realTime = realTime;
356        result.measuredOps = operations;
357    }
